# Task Manager

A simple command-line Task Manager application written in Python.

## Features

* Add a mission
* List all missions
* Mark a mission as completed
* Store missions in a text file
* Simple menu system

## Technologies

* Python
* File Handling
* Functions
* Dictionaries
* Exception Handling

## How to Run

```bash
python main.py
```

## Example

1 - Add Mission
2 - List Missions
3 - Complete Mission
4 - Exit
